TY  - JOUR
TI  - Non-Convexifiable Pareto Sets
AU  - Kannai, Yakar
AU  - Mantel, Rolf
AB  - [The existence of comprehensive sets in R^3 which cannot be transformed onto convex sets by means of ordinal transformations (i.e., continuous, strictly increasing transformations of the coordinate axes) is established. Such sets can be realized as the disposable hulls of pure exchange economies with convex preference orderings.]
