TY  - JOUR
TI  - The Heteroscedastic Linear Model: Exact Finite Sample Results
AU  - Taylor, William E.
AB  - [For the two sample linear heteroscedastic regression model, moments of a popular two stage Aitken estimator are derived analytically. Even for small samples and/or near homoscedastic errors, the two stage procedure is surprisingly efficient relative to both unweighted least squares and the Gauss-Markov estimator. These exact results are compared with the author's previous calculations derived from Nagar approximations.]
