TY  - JOUR
TI  - Double k-Class Estimators of Coefficients in Linear Regression
AU  - Ullah, Aman
AU  - Ullah, Shobha
AB  - [This paper develops a new family of biased estimators, namely the double k-class, for the parameters of the general linear regression model. We note that James and Stein[7] Stein-rule estimator in the regression context is a member of the family of double k-class. The conditions for the existence of the moments and expressions for the exact and approximate bias, moment matrix, and the risk function of the double k-class estimator are analyzed.]
